Malice entered the CR room, his heavy footfalls echoing through the hall.  He surveyed the room, and the only ones he recognized was Rodimus Prime and Kup.

Richard Allen &lt;roborick007@...&gt; wrote:: : Kup/Rodimus Prime : :

Kup walks into the CR room to find Rodimus discussing things with the others.
Kup: Roddy, I have someone who will be staying with us who I believe you should see.

Rodimus motions to Kup that he will once he has finished with this discussion.

robert riley &lt;bustercross365@...&gt; wrote:
Malice nods and follows Kup, wondering if he is ready to see Rodimus Prime again.  He then wondered if he was ready to take on Unicron.  He thought maybe accepting this mission was a good idea.
&lt;I should of stayed back in the old base.  My commander would have better informed me of my mission.&gt;

Richard Allen &lt;roborick007@...&gt; wrote:
: : Kup : :

Kup chuckled at this bots eagerness for combat.

Kup: You should relax. Things are calm right now and the main priority is preparing for Unicron&#39;s arrival. If you wish, you could come with me to see Rodimus Prime and the others. I&#39;m sure they are planning action.

Kup heads off for the CR room where he had left the others.


robert riley &lt;bustercross365@...&gt; wrote:
Malice cleaned the room a little and stowed his extra gear.  He then left the room and reported to Kup.
&quot;What do you need me to do now, as I have put my gear away?  Recon?  Geurilla warfare?  What are your orders?&quot;

Richard Allen &lt;roborick007@...&gt; wrote:
: : Kup : :

Kup lead Malice into the base and to a vacant quarters.

Kup: You can stay here. Standerd quarters for a Maximal starship.

Kup motions towards the room with his hand.


robert riley &lt;bustercross365@...&gt; wrote:
Malice returned to robot mode, and looked at the base before answering the Maximal.
&quot;Can&#39;t tell you, its a secret.  My employer says so.&quot;  
He continued to look around, then turned to Kup.
&quot;Show me were I can put my stuff, then I can help you guys out.&quot;




